author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Spobag: German Financial Reporting Enforcement Panel Says 2014 Financial Statements Incorrect
text:
Feb 28 (Reuters) - SPOBAG AG:
* SAID ON TUESDAY GERMAN FINANCIAL REPORTING ENFORCEMENT PANEL (DPR) HAS DETERMINED THAT ANNUAL FINANCIAL STATEMENTS DATED 31.12.2014 AND THE MANAGEMENT REPORT FOR 2014 ARE INCORRECT
